Author: obviouslynotjackie
Text: It does suck :/ there are times when I’m otp with him (he lives in another state) and I’m like ughh I’m getting tired I think we should gts, but the only reason I wanna hang up is bc I have bread and peanut butter and cereal in the kitchen. And the entire time he’s telling me goodnight and that he loves me and he’s gonna miss me, I’m just thinking about the binge foods I’ll eat as soon as we hang up :/
